high_descs: turn to the left twice and go to the end of the hall and turn to the left and take a step and turn right and take a few steps and turn right facing the shelf case
pick up the box from the top of the shelf case
turn to the left and go to the front of the waste basket and turn left and take a step and turn to the right and take a step and turn left and go to the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn around and move forward. Face the box on the left side.
Pick up the box from the shelf along the wall.
Carry the box and turn to the left. Then turn left to locate the tall lamp in the corner.
Hold up the box and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Carry a box to the lamp and turn it on.

high_descs: Turn around and move into the next room. Turn right to face the small brown table.
Pick up the box from the small brown table.
Carry the box and turn to the left. Move all the way back and turn left to find the lamp in the corner.
Hold the box and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Hold a box and turn on the lamp.
